    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308330/extras/746e04404825aeb9266ecb75e719179d.poster.avif?t=1769786492\" width=1170 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308330/extras/746e04404825aeb9266ecb75e719179d.webm?t=1769786492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308330/extras/746e04404825aeb9266ecb75e719179d.mp4?t=1769786492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Desktop Companion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cute creature lives on your screen, wandering around and reacting to your actions as it naps, stretches, and explores while you work, keeping you company throughout the day.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Care &amp; Interaction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a bond with your Chippu through simple, meaningful interactions. Feed it when it’s hungry, pet it to show affection, and play together during breaks. Customize its look with cozy outfits and make it truly yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Productivity Helper</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay focused without pressure. Use Pomodoro sessions, gentle reminders, and a to-do list to structure your day. As you work, your Chippu cheers you on and earns coins, rewards, and little treasures along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Enjoy a cozy desktop companion that reacts to your daily activity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Feed, pet, play, and bond with your creature</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Use Pomodoro timers to earn coins, with reminders and a to-do list </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Customize your Chippu with cute outfits and accessories</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Relax with a pressure-free experience designed for work and study</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308330/extras/852672356df800f9b8babbe2bfbfe4e7.poster.avif?t=1769786492\" width=856 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308330/extras/852672356df800f9b8babbe2bfbfe4e7.webm?t=1769786492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308330/extras/852672356df800f9b8babbe2bfbfe4e7.mp4?t=1769786492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
